The paper deals with unsupervised learning algorithms for mining large text corpora for patterns that express implicit semantic relations. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
